data.title: Charles Maurice de Talleyrand-Périgord
data.meta_description: Author of Memoirs of the Prince de Talleyrand, Memoir concerning the commercial relations of the United States with England, Talleyrand in America as a financial promoter, 1794-96, Ambassade de Talleyrand à Londres, 1830-1834, Correspondance diplomatique de Talleyrand, The correspondence of Prince Talleyrand and King Louis XVIII, Mémoires complets et authentiques de Charles-Maurice de Talleyrand, prince de Bénévent, Mémoires du prince de Talleyrand
